%vlocity_namespace%__InternalNotes__c: The date selected is converted to a value so it can be used by the pricing procedures. This formula field also combines the output of the 2 Request Coverage Effective Date fields into 1

%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.expression:
CONCATENATE(IF(%BrokerProfile% = 'Anthem SG Broker', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Jan') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Feb') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Mar'), 'Q1', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Apr') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'May') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Jun'), 'Q2', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Jul') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Aug') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Sep'), 'Q3', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Oct') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Nov') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Dec'), 'Q4')))),
IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Jan') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Feb') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Mar'), 'Q1', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Apr') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'May') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Jun'), 'Q2', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Jul') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Aug') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Sep'), 'Q3', IF(CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Oct') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Nov') || CONTAINS(SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[0], 'Dec'), 'Q4'))))),'_',
IF(%BrokerProfile% = 'Anthem SG Broker', SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageEffectiveDate%, ' ', 3)[2], SPLIT(%RequestedCoverageNonBrokerDates%, ' ', 3)[2]))

Name: ReqEffDtFormula
